features: Get It All Done With Ease: What a smart & pretty way to organize notes, reminders, to do’s and to turn your ideas into actions! The cute spiral notebook is a fantastic tool for office and home use, for writing down whatever comes to your mind neatly and with style

Plenty Of Space - Even For Loose Notes & Co.: Perfectly sized at 10.6x8.5”, with 110-pages & an extra double-sided storage pocket for loose notes, documents, grocery lists & more - with ZICOTOs’ college ruled notebook journal you have everything neatly in one spot

Beautiful Beige Design: An adorable look that makes it fun to write in! The lovely designed spiral journal notebook features lined inner pages for neat, even and legible writing or in other words: unfettered space to unlock your creativity

Practical Spiral Bound: The paper notebook is a winner! The cute notebook is designed to positively influence your daily life at home or work. The clever spiral binding ensures smooth page turning and keeps pages attached reliably, while still staying flat when opened

Premium Made For Everyday Use: Whether used to jot down notes and tasks, brainstorm, journal or even doodle, thanks to its sturdy cover and premium paper with a perforated edge for easy tear-off, the modern notebook is your durable companion for a long time to come
body.description: Ruled College Notebooks By ZICOTO: Your Must-Have Tool For A Well-Organized Home And Professional Life! 110 pages for you to stay organized neatly, create better habits and ultimately boost your productivity! Thanks to the 10.6x8.5” note book you are all set to tick off your to do’s, projects and co. with newfound ease. The pages in the notebook are all lined for even & legible writing - super practical! Use the beautiful spiral notebook to capture spontaneous ideas, to take notes, brainstorm, make to-do lists, map out a marketing strategy or simply for scribbling down anything that comes to your mind. Whether used at home or at the office, the practical notebook also provides a wonderful opportunity to let your imagination flow and to unleash your creativity - daydreaming, journaling, doodling - let it all unfold. From a cute, simple notebook to pure magic! Beautifully designed with clever features! Do you want to add loose notes, letters, documents or shopping lists? We’ve got you covered! There are two small storage pockets you can use for additional papers & more. The reliable spiral binding makes it even easier to organize your tasks. Flipping the pages is a breeze and you can put the notebook down flat without any hassle. As each page has a perforated edge, it is super easy for you to tear-off any page as necessary. The spiral notebook will be your cherished second brain and with its sturdy cover and premium paper it is a durable tool you will never want to miss again. ***All designs are protected by U.S. Reg. reviews.reviewText: Great quality. Thank you for this beautiful notebook. The paper is smooth and a nice thickness. Not cheaply done. I appreciate the quality of this. Already going to order my next one. A nice journal to have for some self care or a nice note pad, whatever you may need.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My Favorite Journal -Ever!
reviews.reviewText: I am picky about journals and have tried so many but I have to say that this is my favorite one ever! Why? First, I love the size. It's more like the size of a notebook so my hand doesn't fall off the edge when I write. Second, it's spiral bound so it lays completely flat. Third, it's perforated! So, if there are particular pages I want to remove I can do so easily. Fourth, the pages are thicker so when I write with pens it does not bleed through. Fifth, it's simple, aesthetically pleasing, and slips easily into most of my bags. Sixth, the front and back cover are stiff, providing a firm surface even if I'm just writing with it on my lap! Can't say enough good things. If you like journaling try this one!
